I'm the same way but with like anything that penetrates my skin. 😅

Once I broke my phone and got a very small piece of glass stuck in my finger. And when I asked my grandpa for help I started hyperventalating.

My entire family will be like "I'm not gonna touch you I just want to see how bad it is" and I'll just get hysterical.

Long story short I went to sleep with glass in my thumb and went about my day and eventually it was just gone.
